        public static FCell copyCell(FCell from,
                             FCell to)
        Copies the cell-style, cell-type, comment, and value from the source cell to the target cell. If the target cell contains a value it will be overwritten.

        Note: Both cells must be located in the same workbook.

        Parameters:
        from - the source cell
        to - the target cell
        Returns:
        the target cell

      • autoSizeColumn

        public FSheet autoSizeColumn(int index)
        Adjusts the width of the specified column to fit its contents.

        The content of merged cells is ignored.

        This process can be relatively slow on large sheets, so this should normally only be called once per column, at the end of your processing.

        Parameters:
        index - the 0-based column index
        Returns:
        this sheet
        See Also:
        Sheet.autoSizeColumn(int, boolean)

      • autoSizeColumns

        public FSheet autoSizeColumns()
        Adjusts the width of all columns to fit their contents.

        The content of merged cells is ignored.

        This process can be relatively slow on large sheets, so this should normally only be called once per column, at the end of your processing.

        Returns:
        this sheet
        See Also:
        Sheet.autoSizeColumn(int, boolean)
